MATH 523.course_description:
Banach spaces:  review of L^p spaces, linear operators, dual space, Hahn-Banach theorem, weak topologies, Banach-Alaoglu theorem, compact and bounded operators, closed graph theorem;
Hilbert spaces:  self-adjoint and unitary operators (including spectral theorem), symmetric operators and self-adjoint extensions;  if time allows, distributions and Sobolev spaces.
  Repeatable for Credit.
